title: Gorpkeeping with Walter Pearce
description:
Throwing Fits has always been about three things and three things only: 1. super hot chicks, 2. partying and 3. partying with super hot chicks. With that in mind, it should come as no surprise that this week the boys are dialing in Walter Pearce, the co-founder of Midland Agency. Walter is going goat mode off rip for an absolutely instant blassic, covering the model drug du jour, his favorite high-fashion clients, predators and perverts, god level gorp, tips for the boudoir, the art of art direction, succulents, wifing up a world famous international super model and much more on this very buzzy and downtown episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
